18.06.2026

// XA
NOTE READ CUSTOMER ID
GRAB 300
COPY F X
COPY X M
DROP

NOTE ZEROING BALANCE
LINK 800
GRAB 200
MARK READ_FILE
  TEST F = X
    FJMP READ_FILE
  COPY F M
  SEEK -1
  COPY 0 F
  COPY F M
  SEEK -1
  COPY 0 F
  

// XB
NOTE GET DATE
LINK 800
LINK 801
COPY #DATE X
LINK -1

NOTE APPEND PAYMENT LOG
GRAB 201
SEEK 9999
COPY X F
COPY M F
COPY M F
COPY M F